{"tid":421885,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人破解到呢個悖論","createTime":"2017-10-02T15:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T05:48:23.000Z","uid":53698,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"900cb3a88e1473ae824ddd3f6e8a74e1712ae8df","tid":421885,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"其實哩個係一個悖論<br />\n<br />\n睇下以下例子<br />\n<br />\n錢包悖論內容<br />\n<br />\nA和B兩人進行一場賭博。<br />\n<br />\n賭法是：由第三者計算A、B二君錢包裡面的錢，錢少者可以贏走錢多者的錢。<br />\n<br />\nA對於這場賭博的想法為：若B君的錢比我少，我可能輸掉我現有的錢。但若B君的錢比我多，我贏了，就會得到多於我現有的錢。我能夠贏的錢比輸的錢多，所以這場賭博對我有利。<br />\n<br />\n而B的想法也是如此。<br />\n<br />\n二人想法的邏輯都正確，但若認為二人的想法都正確，又將做出這場賭博對A、B二人都有利的錯誤結論。這顯然是一個悖論。<br />\n<br />\n所以話哩個係一個人生哲理問題，你get到幾多就幾多<br />\n<br />\n互勉之"},{"pid":"d4bbeb900638977d5b24872edc9b838c1df12697","tid":421885,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a350e9ee7ff02b12f93fa2657ede32ae7a529dab","tid":421885,"uid":140345,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"獎門人都識啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t1zp9mxi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft1zp9mxi&h=f2ecfdd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"817510f3014b70b0b0e646b1bb0728e0bbc35d28","tid":421885,"uid":51746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"當我手上係法定最低額貨幣嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你贏嘅機會係0呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78069e5554a3d024205b8c2d5df2b66e386895b6","tid":421885,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"佢地可以隨意揀放幾多錢入去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46de3e37c2893eae8ff9d0cc43c5c70ec8b32f7a","tid":421885,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"最後2個都0蚊 打和啦super<br />\n冇悖論<br />\n正常人都會得出呢個game 係冇野贏<br />\n即係跟本點諗相方都冇利可途<br />\n就好似過3關 識玩 和硬<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔識玩"},{"pid":"3389d9dae26e327e4e297cf6da2236fd15ebbd55","tid":421885,"uid":140141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"唔明點解個遊戲會對自己有利 如果贏當然係可以拎比自己多啲錢 但如果輸(假如A輸) 咁即係A比B 有更多錢 A咪比B輸得更多錢 咁即係相對地會對自己不利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有錯請指教"},{"pid":"a3aac6c3082b6098798236c7e86ed869ec7512d8","tid":421885,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2205db0d2fa28c92e1c35e422cc7a17934167f6d","tid":421885,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6a36f318c8355cfedc3ef4963a5050ce5d25ebc","tid":421885,"uid":121476,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:05:56.000Z","msg":"試下解<br />\n<br />\n假設錢多少係隨機, 即係50/50機會嬴/輸<br />\n輸賭的outcome = -多錢, 嬴的outcome= +多錢<br />\nexpected value = 0.5*(-多錢) + 0.5*多錢=0<br />\n即係對雙方黎講呢個game根本係打和, 唔係有利or不利"},{"pid":"54f9d0268dc60fac871cac79b50daf7136ef46bf","tid":421885,"uid":28031,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:12:33.000Z","msg":"四個字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本多終勝</span></span>"},{"pid":"8910bd8cc548ab3044c62822373d56352ffa87e6","tid":421885,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"係第三者角度係一個零和遊戲<br />\n亦都唔會用佢地自己既邏輯係推論個遊戲係對邊個有利"},{"pid":"c8faf32b38556cf28eb1a9f0717264bcfe58dde2","tid":421885,"uid":80567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T21:25:38.000Z","msg":"-你誤解咩叫悖論(paradox)<br />\n-有興趣去讀博奕論(game theory)<br />\n-自私選擇唔guarantee有利結果架播，咁個個諗住贏就贏架拿?你唔好又話係悖論"},{"pid":"a54087c733b57e540c82951beec304f03d0e55a0","tid":42